cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is about machine translation and the evaluation metric BLEU. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the challenges and variations in reporting BLEU scores, which could fall under the categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions the parsing community, which could suggest a connection to cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
